	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64679426"><p>...but I dare say in all software.</p><p>Which raises the question why software offered to the public is not mandated to be Open Sourced, so it _can_ be checked for problems at all.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64679426">
